		<item>
		<title>Visit to the National Library of Scotland</title>
		<link>https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2016/05/visit-to-the-national-library-of-scotland.html</link>
					<comments>https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2016/05/visit-to-the-national-library-of-scotland.html#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[RobJN]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 27 May 2016 21:49:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Observations]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.mappa-mercia.org/?p=1407</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Last October I had the pleasure of visiting the National Library of Scotland. I was up in Edinburgh at State of the Map Scotland and couldn&#8217;t pass up on the opportunity to have a guided tour of the library&#8217;s maps &#8230; <a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2016/05/visit-to-the-national-library-of-scotland.html">Continued</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Last October I had the pleasure of visiting the National Library of Scotland. I was up in Edinburgh at <a href="http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/State_of_the_Map_Scotland_2015" target="_blank">State of the Map Scotland</a> and couldn&#8217;t pass up on the opportunity to have a guided tour of the library&#8217;s maps reading room. Our host, Chris Fleet, had laid out a number of fantastic items from their collection &#8211; each with it&#8217;s own story.</p>
<p>Being a bit of a map geek I took way too many photos during the hour or so we had before closure. Here are some of the best to whet your appetite. The NLS are long term <a href="http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/National_Library_of_Scotland" target="_blank">supporters of OpenStreetMap</a>, have scanned and georeferenced many thousands of maps, and host zoomable maps on their <a href="http://maps.nls.uk/index.html" target="_blank">amazing website</a>. If you find yourself in Edinburgh, be sure to check out their collection.</p>
<div id="attachment_1408" style="width: 810px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1408" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1408" src="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized000.jpg" alt="Russian military maps (read all about these secret cold war maps)." width="800" height="600" srcset="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized000.jpg 800w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized000-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized000-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><p id="caption-attachment-1408" class="wp-caption-text">Russian military maps (link: <a href="http://www.wired.com/2015/07/secret-cold-war-maps/" target="_blank">secret cold war maps</a>).</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1409" style="width: 810px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1409" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1409" src="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized003.jpg" alt="Textured maps for the blind and partially sighted." width="800" height="600" srcset="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized003.jpg 800w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized003-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized003-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><p id="caption-attachment-1409" class="wp-caption-text">Textured maps for the blind and partially sighted.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1410" style="width: 810px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1410" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1410" src="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized005.jpg" alt="The Blaeu Atlas of Scotland, 1654 (view online)" width="800" height="600" srcset="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized005.jpg 800w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized005-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/resized005-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><p id="caption-attachment-1410" class="wp-caption-text">The Blaeu Atlas of Scotland, 1654 (<a href="http://maps.nls.uk/view/00000395" target="_blank">view online</a>)</p></div>
